{"tid":1381144,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[公投] 8.4 遍地開花-罷工前夕-七區集會 暨 港島西&新界東夾擊大遊行","createTime":"2019-07-29T07:26:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T13:25:41.000Z","uid":167548,"like":64,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"336e8c375fbce0deae6064cc6c9f3dec39421e5f","tid":1381144,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:26:37.000Z","msg":"請冷靜地細閱我嘅見解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">重申本人支持 8.4 遍地開花 罷工前夕 七區集會</span><br />\n勇武求下你冷靜落嚟睇完再投<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n手足有沒唸過如果今個星期日繼續搞大遊行, <br />\n港島西大遊行好大機會被發出反對通知書,<br />\n點解? 因為班高官會認為你地想搞中聯辦。<br />\n再一次重演 721、728 慘劇 兩次已經捉左起碼50人以上。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">勇武會否上線？ 一定會！</span><br />\n但是現時賽後檢討提出不是盲目勇武，是要具目的性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再一次攻擊中聯辦？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&nbsp;<br />\n其實721突襲已經目的達到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n只不過被元朗恐襲遮蓋晒個成效<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同一時間會有將軍澳大遊行，<br />\n我有三問<br />\n一、你可以保證唔會搶左人流？<br />\n二、會否出現勇武去晒港島西同中聯辦班黑警打過, 和理非去晒將軍澳大遊行？<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我明白其實兩個大遊行搞手已經一次又一次推遲去迎合現況</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最緊要係自從7月開始勇武一直上線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n和理非同一家大細根本出唔到咩力，<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">更重要係你不得不承認會有淺黃麻木。</span><br />\n<br />\n大家一直個方針是和理非 &rarr; 勇武  &rarr; 和理非 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但是現況就是陷入彊局, 勇武繼續升級打落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你置於港共同中共位置唸佢地係可以<span style=\"color: red;\">繼續無視</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">同埋出水炮車啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n728清場射左幾多百發子彈</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">在此呼籲大家冷靜落嚟,<br />\n罷工要徹底成功, 靠嘅是和理非港豬！<br />\n今個星期日8.4 舉行  遍地開花-<span style=\"color: red;\">罷工前夕</span>-七區集會<br />\n先能夠號召千千萬萬香港人！<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">支持 8.4 遍地開花 罷工前夕 七區集會 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kkJc5rX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkkJc5rX.jpg&h=ba4f8015&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">支持 8.4 東西夾擊大遊行 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EkvyPTR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEkvyPTR.jpg&h=b62f6252&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"941a58c53cd36b78d25b32052028ba95faf2418f","tid":1381144,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:27:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd4f4780f44b9eee75a405398b1fb3af328eb6c0","tid":1381144,"uid":167548,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:27:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbae0626699eb7ec3970384f553a05586f2bf307","tid":1381144,"uid":167548,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:29:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e9d40b0305b39338c8a665faef328d6d4daaa8f","tid":1381144,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07: